decl: example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnOdd fun x ↦ f x * g x
og_raw:
example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnOdd fun x ↦ f x * g x  := by
  intro x
  dsimp
  rw [ef, og, neg_mul_eq_mul_neg]
new_raw:
example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnOdd fun x ↦ f x * g x  := by
  intro x
  dsimp
  rw [ef, og, neg_mul_eq_mul_neg]

decl: example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnEven fun x ↦ f (g x)
og_raw:
example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnEven fun x ↦ f (g x)  := by
  intro x
  dsimp
  rw [og, ← ef]
new_raw:
example (ef : FnEven f) (og : FnOdd g) : FnEven fun x ↦ f (g x)  := by
  intro x
  dsimp
  rw [og, ← ef]

decl: example : r ⊆ s → s ⊆ t → r ⊆ t
og_raw:
example : r ⊆ s → s ⊆ t → r ⊆ t  := by
  intro rsubs ssubt x xr
  apply ssubt
  apply rsubs
  apply xr
new_raw:
example : r ⊆ s → s ⊆ t → r ⊆ t  := by
  rintro rsubs ssubt x xr
  exact ssubt (rsubs xr)

decl: example (h : SetUb s a) (h' : a ≤ b) : SetUb s b
og_raw:
example (h : SetUb s a) (h' : a ≤ b) : SetUb s b  := by
  intro x xs
  apply le_trans (h x xs) h'
new_raw:
example (h : SetUb s a) (h' : a ≤ b) : SetUb s b  := by
  intro x xs
  exact le_trans (h x xs) h'

decl: example {c : ℝ} (h : c ≠ 0) : Injective fun x ↦ c * x
og_raw:
example {c : ℝ} (h : c ≠ 0) : Injective fun x ↦ c * x  := by
  intro x₁ x₂ h'
  apply (mul_right_inj' h).mp h'
new_raw:
example {c : ℝ} (h : c ≠ 0) : Injective fun x ↦ c * x  := by
  intro x₁ x₂ h'
  exact (mul_right_inj' h).mp h'

decl: example (injg : Injective g) (injf : Injective f) : Injective fun x ↦ g (f x)
og_raw:
example (injg : Injective g) (injf : Injective f) : Injective fun x ↦ g (f x)  := by
  intro x₁ x₂ h
  apply injf
  apply injg
  apply h
new_raw:
example (injg : Injective g) (injf : Injective f) : Injective fun x ↦ g (f x)  := by
  intro x₁ x₂ h
  apply injf (injg h)
